Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:25.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We went through the trouble of rushing here and she’s not home!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are, student council president! \NJust where were you? Geez!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering, what’s that tablet in your hands for?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You actually admit it!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I feel like we’re so used to it now…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,To a talking box…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Do you like this brand?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.61,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What even makes a good box?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:25.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um. So that means…?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,….Sachi…senpai…?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:05.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What time is it?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:40.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I see.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… see.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.67,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Personally, I–\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.29,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Oh, you awake?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:08.90,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Around 4:00 in the afternoon.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:10.51,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But anyway…\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I swear, that girl’s just like a cat.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:35.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,She might’ve decided to come over, but I have no idea.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:46.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Sachi-senpai, it looks like she’s been messing with the first-years.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:48.56,Megumi,,0,0,0,,She gave them “tests,”\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,and she’s been making them do all sorts of things.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:02:00.52,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I figured I’d just wait and see what happens, but what do you think, Kozue?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.07,NPC,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\fs35}[Kaho & Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:42.86,NPC,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs35}[Kaho & Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Where is she!?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:49.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It is what it is, so I’ll let it slide this time, I guess!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What is any of this supposed to mean…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.65,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So you really are planning on taking it away from us!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yaaay.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I was feelin’ pretty tired, actually–\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:16.88,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}This should be good.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.78,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Open!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Phew. Yay!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.95,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That was really comfy!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:06.66,Sachi,,0,0,0,,And… there.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:10.90,Sachi,,0,0,0,,To think Kozue of all people would catch a cold…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.94,Sachi,,0,0,0,,That’s not something you see often.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:17.43,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…There’s a pretty good chance you’ll feel better by the Rindou Festival, but…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.07,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Get well soon.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.21,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s waiting for you.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.10,Sachi,,0,0,0,,But still…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:28.26,Sachi,,0,0,0,,all of them really said that they were doing this “for the second-years,” huh…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.22,Sachi,,0,0,0,,They must really love you three.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:34.24,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You found yourself some real nice girls, you know.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:38.24,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I thought I did pretty well with the three I got, but…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.62,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Kozue. Not bad.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:46.35,Sachi,,0,0,0,,…I can’t wait to see you win Love Live!, Kozue.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:24.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Did Sachi-senpai come over?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.71,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, you’re already here?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.13,Sachi,,0,0,0,,That was quick.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.05,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.05,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of stuff to do in the schoolyard…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:45.98,Sachi,,0,0,0,,so I’m sorry…?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:50.98,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Thanks…?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.93,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.64,Sachi,,0,0,0,,It’s for preparing the stage for the festival.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:03.68,Sachi,,0,0,0,,See?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:13.44,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha! It’d be pretty rough if you didn’t like this kinda thing, huh!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.57,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:27.84,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Creating the stage, decorating the location, and preparing everything based on what whoever’s using it wants…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.84,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Guess I really like stuff like that.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:36.30,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Though I am still taking that stage away from your club.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.45,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.64,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Now, if you want me to return that stage to you–\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:50.60,Sachi,,0,0,0,,wait, if you’re here, then that means…?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.73,Sachi,,0,0,0,,That means you’ve uploaded the video, then?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.54,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can sit down.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.91,Sachi,,0,0,0,,I got sweets for you.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.69,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I had a box prepared, just for you.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.05,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Hehehe…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.89,Sachi,,0,0,0,,‘Kay, I’m gonna watch your video now.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.13,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Take it easy for a bit.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.47,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Kinda, yeah.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:38.15,Sachi,,0,0,0,,But it’s not just me, your second-years like it, too.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.24,Sachi,,0,0,0,,It was actually one of Tsuzuri’s favorites.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.02,Sachi,,0,0,0,,She’s the one that told me about it.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.18,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Hm?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.13,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Wait, did I say something just now?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.34,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Oh…\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.91,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Alright, I’m done watching your video!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.06,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Time to announce the results of your second test!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.41,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.27,Sachi,,0,0,0,,As you know, the second test was to make a video advertising your club!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.36,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Seeing as you made it, you’ve passed!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.07,Sachi,,0,0,0,,And the actual video was good, too!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.99,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Kaho, I like how you got directly to the point.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.79,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You want to blossom.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.17,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think that’s perfect!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.29,Sachi,,0,0,0,,You too, Rurino.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.57,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Because it’s fun, huh?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:37.87,Sachi,,0,0,0,,It’s clear that as a first-year, you’re going to keep having fun as a school idol.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.01,Sachi,,0,0,0,,That’s also very good!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:49.99,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Hm.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.00,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Looks like I found a really good box.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.35,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Now, Sayaka.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:03.19,Sachi,,0,0,0,,–There’s a lot of school idols that don’t compete in Love Live!, you know?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.42,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Love Live! isn’t the only thing school idols exist for.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:15.98,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Of course, a lot of school idols share the goal of appearing in Love Live!,\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.29,Sachi,,0,0,0,,but it’s not as if they have no choice but to.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.81,Sachi,,0,0,0,,It’s not simply a matter of being competitors.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:26.80,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Sayaka.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.31,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Why is Love Live!--\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.00,Sachi,,0,0,0,,No, let me rephrase.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.83,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to be a school idol?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.09,Sachi,,0,0,0,,What’s your reason?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.59,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Kaho and Rurino pass.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.69,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Honestly, they don’t even have to take the third test.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:47.34,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Sayaka, I’m giving you your third test!\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.64,Sachi,,0,0,0,,–Why did you become a school idol?\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.96,Sachi,,0,0,0,,Give me your answer.\N{\fs35}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.96,Sachi,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:30.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,N-No, I don’t think she actually lives here…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:54.06,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don’t think you actually need to apologize for that…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean you…?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:54.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, we’ve completed your second test…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that…?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.33,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. It was just that part about Tsuzuri-senpai liking these sweets.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’re just trying to change the subject, aren’t you!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.65,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, you’re fully recharged now?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.14,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.28,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Huh?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.17,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.77,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Did you have a dream about someone?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.81,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I dunno.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.26,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay leaving it to her?\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
